name: stapply
description: Stapply, an AI job search engine that goes beyond search
readme_summary: Stapply is an AI-powered job search engine that crawls and indexes jobs, leveraging AI to rerank and validate search results based on user criteria. It also automates job applications using an AI agent that autofills forms and uploads resumes, with both cloud and local versions available.
key_features: Automated job application using AI agent
Browser Use for live job search
primary_use_case: Finding and applying for jobs that closely match user criteria using AI-powered search and automation.
cover_image_prompt: Imagine a skilled artisan meticulously crafting personalized keys, each uniquely shaped to unlock a specific door representing a dream job. The artisan uses a glowing AI lens to analyze blueprints (job descriptions) and forge keys that perfectly fit. Behind the artisan, a vast wall of doors shimmers with potential. Subtle UI elements float nearby, displaying job titles and company logos. The scene is set in a bright, futuristic workshop with a focus on precision and personalization. The image should be in a 3D isometric illustration style with vibrant colors and sharp details.

name: proxypin
description: Open source free capture HTTP(S) traffic  software ProxyPin, supporting full platform systems
readme_summary: ProxyPin is an open-source tool for capturing and inspecting HTTP(S) traffic across multiple platforms (Windows, Mac, Android, iOS, Linux). It allows users to intercept, inspect, and rewrite network traffic, making it suitable for debugging, testing, and analyzing network communications, especially for Flutter applications.
primary_use_case: Capturing, inspecting, and modifying HTTP(S) traffic for debugging and analysis across various platforms.
cover_image_prompt: A detective wearing a magnifying glass, examining network packets flowing through a city made of interconnected servers. The detective intercepts and analyzes the packets, rewriting some with a digital pen. Small screens display UI elements of ProxyPin, showing traffic logs and filtering options. The city glows with digital particles, highlighting the flow of data. The repository name, 'ProxyPin,' is subtly displayed on a building. The scene is set at night with a blue and purple color scheme and dramatic lighting. The image should be in a digital painting style with clean lines and clear details.

name: helium
description: Private, fast, and honest web browser
readme_summary: Helium is a Chromium-based web browser focused on privacy and user experience. It aims to provide a fast, unbiased, and bloat-free browsing experience by default, incorporating features like ad-blocking and a focus on user privacy. The project provides builds for macOS, Linux, and Windows.
primary_use_case: General web browsing with enhanced privacy and a clean user experience.
cover_image_prompt: A skilled shipwright carefully constructing a sleek, modern sailboat in a high-tech workshop. The sailboat represents the Helium browser, known for its speed and privacy. The shipwright uses advanced tools to ensure the boat is free of any unnecessary components or bloat. Digital blueprints and UI elements float around the workshop, subtly connecting the metaphor to software. The scene is set in a brightly lit, clean workshop with a focus on precision and craftsmanship. The composition is clean and focused with a blue and white color scheme. The image should be in 3D isometric illustration style with rich details.

name: khal
readme_summary: Khal is a command-line calendar application that allows users to manage and synchronize calendars. It stores events in the vdir format, enabling synchronization with CalDAV servers and other programs using vdirsyncer. The application provides a fast and easy way to add new events and browse/edit calendars through its interactive mode (ikhal).
key_features: Synchronization with CalDAV servers via vdirsyncer
primary_use_case: Managing and synchronizing calendars from the command line, particularly with CalDAV servers.
cover_image_prompt: A skilled clockmaker meticulously assembling a large, intricate calendar using gears representing different events and dates. The calendar is connected to a central server depicted as a glowing network hub, symbolizing synchronization. The clockmaker uses command-line tools projected onto the calendar's surface to adjust and manage the schedule. Small UI elements showing calendar views and event details are subtly integrated into the gears. The scene is set in a brightly lit workshop with a clean, organized layout. The image should be in a 3D isometric illustration style with vibrant colors and clear details.

name: superduper
description: Superduper: End-to-end framework for building custom AI applications and agents.
readme_summary: Superduper is an end-to-end framework designed for building custom AI applications and agents. It facilitates the integration of AI models directly into databases, enabling the creation of database-integrated AI agents and applications using familiar tools. The framework supports various database backends and offers plugins for different use cases.
key_features: Support for multiple database backends (MongoDB, SQL, Snowflake, Redis)
Tools for building custom AI applications and agents
primary_use_case: Building AI-powered applications that directly interact with and leverage data stored in databases.
cover_image_prompt: A skilled architect standing before a blueprint-covered table, seamlessly integrating glowing AI models into the foundation of a towering skyscraper representing a database. The architect carefully connects data streams flowing from the database to the AI models, creating a harmonious structure. Small UI elements showing database queries and model outputs float around the scene. The setting is a brightly lit, futuristic design studio. The composition is clean and focused with a blue and green color scheme. The image should be in 3D isometric illustration style with rich details and vibrant colors.
